VALID=0: Global variable that considers if input is valid

$NAME =~ ^[A-Za-z]+$ : Regular expression, check characters in
NAME to be alphabetical, upper and lowercase

^ : start from beginning of string

+ : whatever is inside the brackets, there must be at
 least one, can be more

 $ : string must end here

 $AGE =~ ^[0-9]+$ : Checks input if numerical
